525
00:42:08.541 --> 00:42:09.375
Hell yeah.

526
00:42:09.458 --> 00:42:12.250
But this is ridiculous.
You're all gonna die.

527
00:42:12.333 --> 00:42:15.541
You wanna go back. go back.
I suggest you do it quick.

528
00:42:18.583 --> 00:42:19.666
<i>Nichiiwad.</i>

529
