551
00:43:33.583 --> 00:43:36.791
You weren't a happy camper. were you?
When he fired you?

552
00:43:37.791 --> 00:43:38.708
No. I...

553
00:43:38.791 --> 00:43:39.791
Look. just...

554
00:43:41.083 --> 00:43:44.791
I've never seen a Kenworth
with less than 10K on the odometer

555
