just up and quit. have you?

556
00:43:47.333 --> 00:43:48.333
No.

557
00:43:48.666 --> 00:43:52.791
Most diesel engines don't seize
on their own unless they burn gasoline.

558
00:43:54.833 --> 00:43:55.916
