- I agree. It's nuts.

606
00:47:06.000 --> 00:47:08.125
- Say you're wrong.
- Say we're not.

607
00:47:08.208 --> 00:47:09.500
Say we put it to a vote.

608
00:47:09.583 --> 00:47:10.958
