- They mean decreasing their number.

623
00:48:05.958 --> 00:48:06.791
Well. how?

624
00:48:06.875 --> 00:48:07.958
How do you think?

625
00:48:09.208 --> 00:48:10.208
No.

626
00:48:10.958 --> 00:48:11.958
