630
00:48:29.500 --> 00:48:31.833
Gurty and I are gonna go check the loads.

631
00:48:31.916 --> 00:48:33.208
then we'll push on.

632
00:48:35.541 --> 00:48:36.625
How's she looking?

633
00:48:50.541 --> 00:48:51.541
Hey! Hey!

634
00:48:52.125 --> 00:48:53.750
- Hey!
- Help! Hey!

635
00:48:55.000 --> 00:48:58.041
