711
00:57:55.833 --> 00:57:57.416
Gurty? Gurty?

712
00:57:58.500 --> 00:57:59.500
Gurty!

713
00:58:00.875 --> 00:58:01.875
Gurty?

714
00:58:02.458 --> 00:58:03.458
Gurty!

715
01:00:03.791 --> 01:00:05.500
Come on. Gurty. Come on.

716
01:00:05.583 --> 01:00:07.250
